Subject: [TRUB] World Beer Festival
Content-Type: text/plain

What did everyone think of the World Beer Festival?

The smaller size was, in my opinion, OK.  I did more true "tasting" and did not finish the day as "jolly" as in years past.

My favorites were all the beers from Cottonwood in Boone NC and the new Lager from Carolina Brewing Company in Holly Springs NC.

-Gary
